snippet.description:
Everyone’s coming over. And you’re invited, too.

At Netflix House, you can explore immersive experiences that take you inside the story, grab a meal inspired by your fave shows at NETFLIX BITES, or stop by our shop to bring your favorite character home (in t-shirt form) – it’s your show now.

Netflix House Philadelphia opens November 12.
Netflix House Dallas opens December 11.

https://netflixhouse.com

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
